{"root":{"data":{"id":"dgvb99egoio0","created":1772760801599,"text":"生成报价"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgvb9hf174w0","created":1772760819047,"text":"预申请付款"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgvba7xhbu00","created":1772760876759,"text":"直接取消报价"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgvbato84so0","created":1772760924089,"text":"同步取消预申请付款intent"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgvbabei1hs0","created":1772760884319,"text":"编辑报价"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgvbby31qq80","created":1772761012056,"text":"同步取消预申请付款intent，基于编辑后的内容允许重新提起预申请付款"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgvba87o4hc0","created":1772760877375,"text":"报价审核部分通过"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgvbc856b8o0","created":1772761033953,"text":"不影响预申请付款intennt"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgvbaquzyf40","created":1772760917968,"text":"报价审核通过"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgvbeav3v3s0","created":1772761196603,"text":"生成采购单，直接调用Airwallex提起付款"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgvbh2cwvjc0","created":1772761413181,"text":"正常支付成功"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgvbh3vyo9s0","created":1772761416510,"text":"生成采购单后，取消并编辑"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgvbhk5xvpk0","created":1772761451941,"text":"取消原本intent，同时取消已经提交的Airwallex付款申请。\n如果已经付款要提示用户Airwallex已经付款"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgvc7wo277s0","created":1772763516627,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgvb9igxtw80","created":1772760821340,"text":"不预申请付款"},"children":[]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}